# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok poland 's governing party on tuesday presented a draft law that would encourage local authorities to remove street names and monuments that glorify communist rule .
# ::alignments
(p / present-01
      :ARG0 (p2 / party
            :ARG0-of (g / govern-01
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Poland"))))
      :ARG1 (l / law
            :ARG1-of (d / draft-01)
            :ARG0-of (e / encourage-01
                  :ARG1 (a / authority
                        :ARG1-of (l2 / local-02))
                  :ARG2 (r / remove-01
                        :ARG0 a
                        :ARG1 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (n2 / name
                                    :mod (s / street))
                              :op2 (m / monument
                                    :ARG0-of (g2 / glorify-01
                                          :ARG1 (r2 / rule-03
                                                :ARG0 (p3 / political-movement
                                                      :name (n3 / name
                                                            :op1 "communism")))))))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok al sadd of qatar launched its asian champions league campaign on wednesday with a #-# win over al ahli of the united arab emirates .
# ::alignments
(l / launch-01
      :ARG0 (c / city
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "al"
                  :op2 "Sadd")
            :part-of c
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Qatar"))
      :ARG1 (c2 / campaign-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (l2 / league
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Asia"
                        :op2 "Champions")))
      :ARG2 (w / win-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 c
            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "al"
                  :op2 "Ahli")
            :part-of (c3 / country-region
                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "United"
                        :op2 "Arab"
                        :op3 "Emirates")))
      :time (w2 / wednesday))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok dr. edgar andrew bering jr. , a pediatric neurosurgeon and researcher who devised a blood-clotting wound dressing widely used on combat casualties in world war ii , died on thursday at his summer home in <unk> , maine .
# ::alignments
(d / die-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Dr."
                  :op2 "Edgar"
                  :op3 "Bering"
                  :op4 "Jr.")
            :mod (n2 / neurosurgeon
                  :mod (p2 / pediatrics))
            :ARG0-of (d2 / devise-01
                  :ARG1 (d3 / dressing
                        :mod (w / wound)
                        :ARG1-of (u / use-01
                              :ARG2 (c / casualty
                                    :mod (c2 / combat-01)
                                    :time (w2 / war
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "World"
                                                :op2 "War"
                                                :op3 "II")))
                              :ARG1-of (w3 / wide-02))))
            :ARG0-of (r / research-01))
      :time (d4 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :location (h / home
            :time d4
            :season (s / summer))
      :location (c3 / city
            :name (n4 / name
                  :op1 "Maine")))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok president barack obama has declared the swine flu outbreak a national emergency , allowing hospitals and local governments to speedily set up alternate sites and procedures if needed to handle any surge of patients , the white house said saturday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "White"
                  :op2 "House"))
      :ARG1 (d / declare-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Barack"
                        :op2 "Obama")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
            :ARG1 (o / outbreak-29
                  :ARG1 (d2 / disease
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "swine"
                              :op2 "flu")))
            :ARG2 (e / emergency
                  :mod (n4 / nation))
            :ARG0-of (a / allow-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / set-up-03
                        :ARG0 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (h2 / hospital)
                              :op2 g
                              :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01)
                              :ARG1-of (l / local-02)))
                  :ARG1 (a3 / and
                        :op1 (s3 / site
                              :mod (a4 / alternate))
                        :op2 (p3 / procedure))
                  :manner (s4 / speedy)
                  :condition (n5 / need-01
                        :ARG0 a2
                        :ARG1 s2
                        :purpose (h3 / handle-01
                              :ARG0 a2
                              :ARG1 (s5 / surge-01
                                    :ARG1 (p4 / person
                                          :ARG0-of (h4 / have-rel-role-91
                                                :ARG2 (p5 / patient)))
                                    :mod (a5 / any))))))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (s6 / saturday)))

                        :ARG0 (p2 / person
                              :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG2 (o / official)))
                        :ARG1 (c2 / country)
                        :prep-as (o2 / official)))
            :op2 (b2 / become-01
                  :ARG1 (ii / involve-01
                        :ARG1 (p3 / police)
                        :ARG2 (s3 / scandal
                              :topic (l2 / labor-01
                                    :ARG1 (s4 / slave))
                              :ARG1-of (w / widen-01)))
                  :ARG2 (e / evident
                        :ARG2-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                              :ARG1 ii
                              :ARG3 (m / more)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s5 / sunday)))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (m / meteorologist
            :ARG0-of (e / examine-01
                  :ARG1 (c / condition
                        :ARG0-of (s2 / spawn-01
                              :ARG1 (a / and
                                    :op1 (h / hurricane
                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "Rita"))
                                    :op2 (h2 / hurricane
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "Katrina")))))))
      :ARG1 (l / likely-01
            :ARG1 (h3 / hurricane
                  :ARG1-of (ii / intense-02)
                  :mod (a2 / another)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :month 11))
            :ARG1-of (s3 / strong-02)))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (w / wednesday))
            :location (f / fountain
                  :consist-of (s / stake
                        :mod (y / youth))
                  :location (p / park
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Gulfstream"))))
      :op2 (m2 / mission-01
            :ARG1 (t2 / try-01
                  :ARG1 (c5 / catch-01
                        :ARG1 (s2 / song
                              :poss (p2 / person
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Unbridled"))
                              :ARG1-of (f2 / favor-01
                                    :ARG0 (g2 / game
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Kentucky"
                                                :op2 "Derby"))))))

                  :quant 9
                  :unit (y2 / year))))

                                          :polarity -))
                              :op2 (b2 / barrier
                                    :mod (t2 / tariff
                                          :polarity -)))

                        :ARG1 (p / power
                              :mod (h / hydro)

                                    :op1 (c4 / company
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Nepal"))

                                                :op1 "Bhutan")))))

# ::alignments
(l / launch-01
      :ARG0 (a / airline
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Vietnam")))
      :ARG1 (c2 / campaign-01
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (p / promote-02))
      :time (j / just)
      :manner (o / offer-01
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (d / discount-01
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (p2 / percentage-entity
                        :value "#.")
                  :ARG3 (p3 / passenger
                        :ARG0-of (f / fly-01
                              :ARG2 (b / between
                                    :op1 (c3 / city
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "Ho"
                                                :op2 "Chi"
                                                :op3 "Minh")
                                          :poss c)
                                    :op2 (c4 / city
                                          :location (c5 / continent
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Europe"))
                                          :ARG1-of (m / major-02))))))
            :ARG3 (a2 / airfare)))
